    %% High Availability Principles
    %% =====================================================

    Principles["High Availability Principles

• No Single Point of Failure
• Stateless Control Plane
• Horizontally Scalable APIs
• Relay Redundancy
• Persistent Agent Reconnection
• Shared Durable State
• Automatic Health Checks
• Rolling Upgrades
• Failure Isolation"]

    Principles -.-> Control
    Principles -.-> Relay

